divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking photos of a water fall in the west side of Palm Springs didn't see or hear anything when I uploaded the photo I noticed it. My camera lens was clean it was on and off raining but not raining at the time of the photo being taken. I was at the end of a street near the end of Alajo st. in Palm Springs facing San Jacinto Mountain.
